This character is one of the backroom staff at the Moonstone Mask. He stays in his room unless the place is closed down.

He has separete selected for male of female players, as well as differing reactions for charisma of female players.

His dialogue loops in on itself as he engages in small talk to the player. There is in incrementing local on that dialogue, and once it has reached a certain number, the player can initiate a fade to black sexual encounter. Girls Gone Wild. How high the number is (the number of loops spent in small talk) depends on the charisma of the player. The local is hereafter identified as the "SmallTalk" local

If the SmallTalk local gets too low, he will set another local that marks him as unfriendly, and will switch to the starting condition appropriate for that.
